<p class="ayah 39-8" id="8" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ وَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَسَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">touches</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] man</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ضُرٌّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">adversity,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَعَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he calls</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) his Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُنِيبًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">turning</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Him;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَوَّلَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He bestows on him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نِعْمَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a favor</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْه