<p class="ayah 39-26" id="26" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَذَاقَهُمُ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So Allah made them taste</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْخِزْىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the disgrace</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَيَوٲةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the life</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلدُّنْيَا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the world,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَعَذَابُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and certainly (the) punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَخِرَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Hereafter</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَكْبَرُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) greater,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْلَمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">knew.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>26<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 39-27" id="27" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ضَرَبْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We have set forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلنَّاسِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">this</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقُرْءَانِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Quran</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَثَلٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">example</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّعَلَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so that they may</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتَذَكَّرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">take heed.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>27<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 39-28" id="28" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُرْءَانًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">A Quran</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَرَبِيًّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) Arabic</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَيْرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">without</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِوَجٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">crookedness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّعَلَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that they may</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتَّقُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">become righteous.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>28<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
