<p class="ayah 39-39" id="39" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰقَوْمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O my people!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱعْمَلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Work</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(according) to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَكَانَتِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your position,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">indeed, I am</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَـٰمِلٌ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">working;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَسَوْفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then soon</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعْلَمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will know</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>39<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
