<p class="ayah 39-41" id="41" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed We,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنزَلْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We revealed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكِتَـٰبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Book</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلنَّاسِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for [the] mankind</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْحَقِّ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in truth.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمَنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱهْتَدَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">accepts guidance,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلِنَفْسِهِۦ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then (it is) for his soul;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ضَلَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">goes astray</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِنَّمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then only</span></span><span class="word stat