 rtl" dir="rtl">قَضَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He has decreed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَوْتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the death,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيُرْسِلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and sends</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأُخْرَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the others</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَجَلٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a term</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّسَمًّى‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">specified.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَأَيَـٰتٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">surely (are) signs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّقَوْمٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for a people</span></span><span class="word staticWord