<p class="ayah 39-43" id="43" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱتَّخَذُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">have they taken</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن دُونِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">besides</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شُفَعَآءَ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">intercessors?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوَلَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Even though</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَمْلِكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">possessing</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَيْــًٔا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">anything,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْقِ