<p class="ayah 39-44" id="44" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُل</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّلَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`To Allah (belongs)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلشَّفَـٰعَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the intercession</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَمِيعًا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">all.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">For Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُلْكُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is the) dominion</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُرْجَعُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will be returned.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>44<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 39-45" id="45" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذُكِرَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah is mentioned</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَحْدَهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Alone,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱشْمَأَزَّتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">shrink with aversion</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلُوبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) hearts</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُؤْمِنُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْأَخِرَةِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in the Hereafter,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذُكِرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">are mentioned</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن دُونِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">besides Him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">behold!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسْتَبْشِرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">rejoice.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>45<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 39-46" id="46" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O Allah!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَاطِرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Creator</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَـٰلِمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Knower</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْغَيْبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the unseen</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلشَّهَـٰدَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the witnessed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">You</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَحْكُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will judge</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">between</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِبَادِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Your slaves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar qu