<p class="ayah 39-52" id="52" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوَلَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Do not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْلَمُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they know</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَبْسُطُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">extends</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرِّزْقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the provision</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَشَآءُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He wills</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَقْدِرُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and restricts.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَأَيَـٰتٍ</span>