<p class="ayah 39-53" id="53" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰعِبَادِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O My slaves!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَسْرَفُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">have transgressed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">against</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنفُسِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">themselves,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَقْنَطُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">despair</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّحْمَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Mercy</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl"