<p class="ayah 39-54" id="54" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنِيبُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And turn</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَسْلِمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and submit</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن قَبْلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">before</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[that]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَأْتِيَكُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">comes to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَذَابُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the punishment;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُنصَرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will be helped.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>5