<p class="ayah 39-69" id="69" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَشْرَقَتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (will) shine</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِنُورِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with (the) light</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) its Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَوُضِعَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (will) be placed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكِتَـٰبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Record</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَجِاْىٓءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (will) be brought</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلنَّبِيِّــۧنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Prophets</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلشُّهَدَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the witnesses,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقُضِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and it (will) be judged</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْنَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">between them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْحَقِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir=