top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَزَنَتُهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">its keepers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Did not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَأْتِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">come to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رُسُلٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Messengers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتْلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">reciting</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَايَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Verses</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) your Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيُنذِرُونَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and warning you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِقَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of the) meeting</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of)